'''Idrissou Mora-Kpai''' (yavutse 14 Nyakanga 1967), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Bene|Bénine]] . <ref name="Ithaca">https://faculty.ithaca.edu/imorakpai/</ref> Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime zizwi cyane ''Indochina Traces of'' the Mother, ''Arlit The Second Paris'', na ''Si-Gueriki Umwamikazi Mama'' . <ref>https://iffr.com/en/persons/idrissou-mora-kpai</ref> Niwe wahawe igihembo cy’igikomangoma cy’Ubuholandi kubera ibyo yagezeho mu buhanzi agamije guteza imbere imibereho myiza mu majyepfo y’isi. <ref name="official">[https://idrimora.com/about/ hthttps://idrimora.com/about/]</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 14 Nyakanga 1967 i Béroubouay, mu majyaruguru ya Bénin mu muryango w'aborozi . Se yari Mora-Kpai Sounon Dangnon naho nyina yari Bougnon Yarou Signangui. <ref>https://theafricainstitute.org/institute-program/idrissou-mora-kpai/</ref>

Yarangije impamyabumenyi ya BA muri kaminuza ya Konrad Wolf Film ya Babelsberg, mu [[Budage]]. Yakoze kandi nk'umwarimu wasuye muri Kaminuza ya Cornell, Kaminuza ya Dukena kaminuza ya Pittsburgh . <ref name="official">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://idrimora.com/about/ "Idrissou Mora-Kpai bio"]. Idrissou Mora-Kpai official website<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">30 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref> Kuri ubu aba muri [[Amerika]]. <ref name="filmuniversitaet">https://www.filmuniversitaet.de/portrait/person/idrissou-mora-kpai</ref> Ni Assistant Professor mu ishami ryitangazamakuru ryubuhanzi, siyanse nubushakashatsi muri Ithaca College . 

== Umwuga ==
Afite imyaka 13, yimukiye i Cotonou maze yiga mu mashuri yisumbuye. Afite imyaka 19, yagiye muri [[Alijeriya]] hanyuma yimukira mu Butaliyani no mu Budage. Hanyuma yize muri Amerika y'Amajyaruguru muri kaminuza yubuntu ya Berlin kuva 1988 kugeza 1993. Amaze kubona impamyabumenyi, yize ibijyanye no gutunganya amashusho muri kaminuza ya Konrad Wolf Film kuva 1994 kugeza 1999. Muri iki gihe cya kaminuza, yakoze firime ebyiri ngufi, ''Transient'' na ''Fake Soldiers'' .  <ref name="filmuniversitaet">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.filmuniversitaet.de/portrait/person/idrissou-mora-kpai "Prof. Idrissou Mora Kpai"]. filmuniversitaet<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">30 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

Mu 1999, Idrissou yimukiye i Paris maze ashinga isosiyete ikora ibintu yitwa 'MKJ Films'. Hamwe n'inzu itunganya, yakoze documentaire ye ya mbere, ''Si-Gueriki'' mu 2002. Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yitabirwa n’amahanga. <ref>http://www.filme-aus-afrika.de/EN/film-database/persons/personen-details/w/399/</ref> Yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime Rotterdam (IFFR), Sinema du Réel, Paris ndetse n’iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Copenhagen (CIFF). Nyuma film yaje guhabwa igihembo cyiza cya Documentaire muri Festival International du Film Francophone de Namur .  <ref name="filmuniversitaet">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.filmuniversitaet.de/portrait/person/idrissou-mora-kpai "Prof. Idrissou Mora Kpai"]. filmuniversitaet<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">30 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

Muri 2019, yakoze film documentaire ''Amerika Street'' . Irasobanura urugamba rwa buri munsi rwumuryango nyafrica wabanyamerika i Charleston, muri Caroline yepfo nyuma yubwicanyi bwa Walter Scott 2015 . Iyi filime yakiriwe neza kandi yerekanwe mu birori byinshi bya firime. <ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/idrissou-mora-kpai/</ref><ref>http://worldcat.org/identities/lccn-no2003129390</ref>

